945
00:52:33,210 --> 00:52:34,628
No.

946
00:52:34,630 --> 00:52:37,647
You taught me that life is about family.

947
00:52:46,106 --> 00:52:49,856
I've tried to make it
home for dinner, but...

948
00:52:51,276 --> 00:52:53,943
[Roman mumbles]

949
