980
00:55:13,067 --> 00:55:14,317
Come, Payton.

981
00:55:15,990 --> 00:55:16,823
Hi.

982
00:55:17,890 --> 00:55:21,057
[children chattering]

983
00:55:24,220 --> 00:55:25,798
Hi Payton. I'm Mary.

984
00:55:25,800 --> 00:55:28,243
