1033
00:59:46,410 --> 00:59:47,523
There was an accident.

1034
00:59:48,730 --> 00:59:51,578
A truck crashed into a utility box.

1035
00:59:51,580 --> 00:59:52,818
Only one man was injured,

1036
00:59:52,820 --> 00:59:55,985
